data.chText: （地球的）半球；（尤指）北半球，南半球
data.enText: one half of the earth, especially the half above or below the equator
one half of a sphere (= a round solid object)

simple_means.memory_skill: hemi 半 + spher 球 + e → 半球

value.def: A hemisphere is one half of the earth.
A hemisphere is one half of the brain.

example.ex: In most people, the left hemisphere is bigger than the right.
example.tran: 多数人的左脑比右脑大。
